{
  "stem": "17299.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were treated like gentlemen in a courtroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- it didn't make sense to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were criminals, but they were not treated like criminals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- on and off altogether for three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went out with a girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a-- Greta [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wolf. ?] She was an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was later on in charge of the typing pool.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of her time, she was interpreter and-- when the German physicians were on trial because she was a registered nurse and midwife in England.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she knew all the medical terms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to date towards this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married her in July 1948.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Gothenburg, Sweden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt very good, but it made me sick that the Germans were let go after so few years in jail.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It did not affect me at all because-- it left me cold because I still had nightmares from it, and I still have on and off.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt that justice was to be done finally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it should have been done in a more radical way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to see the theater in the evening, or we went out taking trips around Nuremberg and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was nothing in Nuremberg I could do, except-- which was illegal for me, and I went anyway with her-- was the American restaurants and things like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was illegal for German and-- and DPs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went with her anyway, because she was a member of the United States Forces at that case.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no friends in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not feel at home there while I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
